high_descs: Turn around and go to the toilet
Pick up the toilet plunger next to the toilet.
Turn left and go to the cabinet.
Put the toilet plunger in the cabinet on the right
anns.task_desc: Put away the toilet plunger in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the plunger on the floor by the toilet.
Pick up the plunger from the floor.
Turn left to face the drawers.
Open the bottom right drawer and put the plunger in it.
anns.task_desc: Move a plunger from the floor to a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room.
Look down and pick up the toilet plunger underneath the towel rack.
Turn to the right and face the cupboards.
Open the cupboard on the right and place the plunger inside behind the toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: To move the plunger to a cabinet.
